title: Sakthi Leelai
subTitle: Sage Bhringi worships only Lord Shiva, Brahma and Vishnu. When Goddess Parvati stands in his way, he goes to the extent of giving rise to a demon.

title: Marudhani
subTitle: Manikam, a teacher, comes to work in a village and stays in Marudhani's house. Later, Marudhani falls in love with him after he protects her dignity.

title: Oru Thaai Makkal
subTitle: A rich man adopts one of the twin sons of his maid after his own child dies. However, fate brings the brothers face to face when they both fall in love with the same woman.

title: Chinna Muthu
subTitle: Chinna Muthu, a valiant young man, opposes the atrocities of rich landlords in his village. His life turns upside down when his sister is impregnated by Sevatha Pandi, a wealthy man.

title: Mamiyargal Jakkirathai
subTitle: Selvi, a young educated girl, gets ill-treated at her husband's house in the name of dowry. Later, she decides to set her mother-in-law straight.

title: Nootrenbadhu
subTitle: A doctor diagnosed with cancer returns to India. There, he meets a journalist who slowly falls in love with him.

title: Uthama Rasa
subTitle: Meenu, a bubbly girl, is in love with Chinnaiya, the village leader. Things change when Marudhu, who is the son of Chinnaiya's rival, Parama Thevar, falls for Meenu.
